==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hurtless
<hw>Hurt"less</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Doing no injury;
harmless; also, unhurt; without injury or harm.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Gentle dame so <qex>hurtless</qex> and so true.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Hurt"less*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Hurt"less*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Husband</ent>⟦br⟧
